318
00:28:25,389 --> 00:28:26,749
- Ayolah.
- Sampai kapan?

319
00:28:32,758 --> 00:28:33,828
Halo?

320
00:28:34,159 --> 00:28:36,128
Ayah, bagaimana Jaksa Kang?

321
00:28:37,628 --> 00:28:38,668
Baiklah.

322
00:28:40,629 --> 00:28:41,669
Aku mengerti.

323
00:28:52,449 --> 00:28:54,408
- Ayah.
- So Young.

324
00:28:54,879 --> 00:28:57,379
Apa wakil jaksa dibunuh oleh benda khusus itu?

325
00:28:57,379 --> 00:28:58,449
Ya.

326
00:28:59,019 --> 00:29:00,118
Dia orangnya.

327
00:29:02,258 --> 00:29:05,429
Saksi yang kuceritakan kemarin ditabrak mobil dan tewas.

328
00:29:06,129 --> 00:29:07,429
Saksinya ditabrak mobil?

329
00:29:07,429 --> 00:29:10,629
Saat para penyelidik Jaksa Han berusaha membawanya,

330
00:29:10,629 --> 00:29:12,299
